    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（休日。俺は千紗とショッピングモールに来ていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(A day off. Chisa and I have come to the shopping mall.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 4.566666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、このスカート……可愛い\nこっちのシャツと合いそう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ this skirt. It’s so cute.\nIt would go well with this shirt…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.633333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "このオフショルも可愛いなぁ……\nこういうのは、芽衣ちゃんに似合いそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This one would look good… worn off the shoulder.\nMei-chan would look so cute in this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 14.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は本当、楽しそうに服を選ぶんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look so happy picking out clothes‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 17.533333333333335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あ、ご……ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Ah‚ I… I’m sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "つい、楽しくなっちゃって……\nはしゃぎ過ぎちゃいましたね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got carried away…\nThis is just so much fun…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 26.066666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（今日、二人で洋服を見に来たのは、千紗の洋服の）\n（コーディネートセンスが仕事に繋がったからだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We’re here looking at clothing today because Chisa’s)\n(great taste has led to a fashion-related job.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.333333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（星見市のフリーペーパーで、千紗が提案する）\n（『着回しテク』が掲載されるというものだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The Hoshimi City free newspaper is going to start a column by Chisa)\n(about fashion techniques.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 37.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも安心して下さいっ\nちゃんと頭の中では、コーデ案考えてますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "P-please‚ don’t worry.\nI’m thinking about outfits in my head‚ promise!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 44.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "たとえば……このブラウスに\nワイドパンツを合わせたカジュアルなコーデとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Take this blouse‚ for example.\nYou could go casual‚ with some wide leg pants.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "こっちのキレイめなワンピースに\nあえてスニーカーを合わせてみたりとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or pair this classy dress\nwith sneakers for contrast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、千紗は自分で試着とかしないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't you ever model them yourself‚ Chisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 60.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 62.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "え……ええ！？　わ、私が……ですか？\n私は、その……試着しても、モデルにならないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… Eh? M-model them… myself?!\nI don’t think… I’d make much of a model.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "それに……{user}さんに見せるのも\nは、恥ずかしいですし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And…I’d also be far too embarrassed\nto show you‚ {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 77.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、無理強いするつもりはないよ。試着した方が\nイメージしやすいんじゃないか、と思っただけだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not going to force you. I just thought\ntrying them on might help you visualize the outfit better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、モデルも千紗がやることになってるんだけど）\n（……分かってるのかな。一応後で確認するか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She’s meant to be modeling for the article.)\n(I’m not sure she realizes. I’ll check with her later.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-02",
      "startTime": 95.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-02",
      "startTime": 95.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-02",
      "startTime": 97.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……\nな、なんだか満喫しちゃいましたね、お買い物",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew…\nT-That was a whole lot of shopping.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-02",
      "startTime": 102.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "最近、レッスンもお仕事も増えてきましたから……\nちょうどいい息抜きになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve had a lot of lessons and work recently…\nThis was a nice break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-02",
      "startTime": 111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "それに……\nすみません、ついでに何着か買って下さって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not to mention…\n…everything you paid for. Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "休日に頑張ってくれたからな。ギャラの現物支給だよ\nそれより、コーディネート案の方はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Consider it payment-in-goods for all your hard work today.\nHow are the outfits looking?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-02",
      "startTime": 122.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。これだけ案があれば\n編集者さんと相談しながら決めていけると思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve got plenty of ideas now. I’ll be able to chat\nwith the editor and whittle them down from here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "なら良かった。記事の完成が楽しみだな\n千紗のセンスと詳しさは、やっぱり凄いよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Great. I can’t wait to read the finished article.\nYou really know your stuff‚ Chisa. Very impressive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-02",
      "startTime": 136.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "……えへへ……\nそんなことないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hee hee…\nI wouldn’t go that far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-02",
      "startTime": 139.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "でも……ファッション誌を読むのは好きでしたから\nそれがこうして活かせるのは……嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’ve always liked reading fashion magazines.\nI’m happy to be able to use that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-02",
      "startTime": 147.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
